'''I Sudutni Asiya''' si o sudutno kotor le [[Asiya|Asikane Barodvipesko]] vi janglo sar o Indikano [[Subbarodvip]]. Kathe si e thema: [[Bangladesh]], [[Bhutan]], [[Bharat]], [[Maldive]], [[Nepal]], [[Pakistan]] thai [[Sri Lanka]]. Vunivar (kana thai kana) vi o [[Afganistan]] ingerdyovel andre.

== Puranipen ==
Kava than si les ek lungo puranipen. Purane chivilizacie barile pashal la [[Sindus (len)|lenyate Sindus]].





















